prompts.frontCover:
A charming cartoon sloth wearing a tiny, lopsided party hat, clinging upside down to a colorful floral vine that frames the top of the card. The sloth is smiling lazily, one eye half-open as if just woken up from a nap. Below the sloth, in the safe center area, is the greeting text written in a beautiful, readable, handwritten cursive script. The entire design is a flat 2D artwork in a whimsical watercolor painting style, featuring soft, flowing colors, artistic brush strokes, visible paper texture, and organic paint bleeds.

Greeting Text:
"I was going to do something wild for your birthday... but then I took a nap."
